Operations

  • PUB /

    Game messages that can be emitted via `socket.emit(eventName, (...args) => {})`

    Accepts one of the following messages:

    • #0exchange_buy

      Purchase an item using exchangeable items

      object
      num
      integer
      name
      string

      The name of the item being purchased

      q
      integer

      The quantity being purchased

      Additional properties are NOT allowed.

      Examples

      {
  "num": 0,
  "name": "string",
  "q": 0
}
      This example has been generated automatically.
    • #1ping_trig

      A ping that requests a `ping_ack` response from the server. Can be used to determine latency

      object
      id
      string

      A unique identifier used to identify the ping event.

      Additional properties are NOT allowed.

      Examples

      {
  "id": "string"
}
      This example has been generated automatically.
